name: The Mouse - Mint
description:
Nocturnal Pastel - Mint
Shedding light on creatures that play in the dark 

Belonging to the Magic of the Night, darkness is no obstacle for the quiet mouse. It is said that a small mouse can go unnoticed, but their bravery is limitless.

Visit the original edit in the neenTAE collection on opensea (Part 3 of Nocturnal Bottone)
